data.description:
Spacious Living Awaits in This Stunning Home!
Step into a world of open living and soaring ceilings in this beautifully designed home. This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom property boasts an open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining friends and family. The high vaulted ceilings create a sense of grandeur and spaciousness, while the abundance of natural light floods the home with warmth. 
Unwind in the heart of the home in the expansive living room. Gather around the fireplace for cozy evenings or enjoy movie nights with the whole gang. The seamless flow leads to the dining area, making it easy to host unforgettable meals. The adjacent kitchen features ample counter space and modern appliances, making cooking a delight.
The split bedroom floor plan offers privacy and tranquility... Retreat to your master suite, a haven featuring a luxurious walk-in shower with floor-to-ceiling tile and a separated double vanity. The remaining bedrooms are well-sized, providing comfortable spaces for family or guests.
Enjoy the Florida lifestyle in the enclosed Florida room. This versatile space is ideal for relaxing with a cup of coffee in the morning or enjoying a glass of wine under the stars. Step outside into the fully fenced-in backyard, where pets can play safely. A large wood storage shed with electricity provides ample storage for your lawn equipment and outdoor tools.
Plumbing and Electrical have been updated 
Beyond the home, a vibrant community awaits. Take advantage of the community pool, playground, tennis and basketball courts, baseball field, and walking path. Stay active, connect with neighbors, and create lasting memories.
